<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <title><%= @title %></title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1><%= @title %></h1>
    <p>Two numbers are called friend if each of them is equal to the sum of all divisors of another, except for this number itself. </p>
    <%= form_with(url: friend_num_path, method: "post", local: false) do |form|%>
        <%= form.label :num, "Enter n: " %>
        <%= form.text_field :num %>
        <div class="button">
            <%= form.submit "Get result" %>
        </div>
    <% end %> 
    <div id="result"></div>
    <script>
        const resultDiv = document.querySelector("#result");
    </script>
</body>
</html>
